heading_context: If you haven’t used the service before
chunks.html_content:
Order DL196 certificates from the Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency (DVSA) online.

Each book contains 25 certificates and costs £200. You need a credit or debit card to order them.

You can only use this service if you’re an approved training body (ATB). Your user ID is ‘ATB’ followed by your ATB number with no spaces.

You must create a new password if you are using this service for the first time.

Your password must be at least 9 characters long. It must include at least 3 of these 4 types of characters:

  • uppercase characters, such as A B C
  • lowercase characters, such as a b c
  • numeric digits, such as 1 2 3
  • special characters, such as £ % &
